</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_537" id="268r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Reinpreht<ex>en</ex></expan> von Walsee, hauptman ob der Ens und
                        hofmeister in Osterreich </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        fürgelegt des Hansen Trospergs, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s,</expan> freunde, wie daz der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> unser
                            <expan>burg<ex>er,</ex></expan> ir freunde, czu Wyen in gefenknüsse
                        kumen sey von sach wegen, die man auf in <expan>auszgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        hab, daran man im doch <expan>ungütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tu und der
                        unschulldig sey. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz ir dem
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige hilff und
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweisen wöllet, daz er ledig werde,
                        als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hertneyde<ex>n</ex></expan> von Potendorff, lantmarschalk czu
                        Osterreich, <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r;</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Leupolt<ex>en</ex></expan> von Eckhartsaw
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r;</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Pylgraun von Pucheim,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Casparn von
                            <expan>Staremb<ex>er</ex>g,</expan>
<expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> czu schawnberg,
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>; und der stat czu Wyen
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> ut
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Reinprechte<ex>n</ex></expan> von Walsee ut
                            <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
